The secretary of the blue party also announced during a press conference two new civic candidates in the lists of Forza Italia at Centro Italia: Graziella Ciriaci, entrepreneur from Marche, and Alessandro Ghinelli, mayor of Arezzo. "The objective of 10% is close," he said. The aim of the forziers is to overcome the League at the June meeting.
