While Salvini continues to reiterate his no to von der Leyen. "I expect concrete answers to citizens and Europeans, I think for example to fishermen, farmers and workers in the automotive sector, do not favor friends appointed as EU sent for SMEs," he remarked. The premier in the door-to-door study explained that the conservatives could also have a candidate for the Commission's presidency. "This is a decision we still have to make," he added. It will be in that case necessary to find agreement with the Poles of Pis and the occasion could arrive at the margin of the next European Council.
