He told Bari the secretary of the Pd, Elly Schlein, from the stage of "Let's go!" in support of the mayor Vito Leccese, supported by the dems, commenting on the choice of the leader of the Movement Five Stars, Giuseppe Conte, to parade from the primaries of the centerleft in Bari on Sunday 7 April.
